sbol:SequenceAnnotation.ns1:title: mSpinach
sbol:SequenceAnnotation.ns1:description: An RNA aptamer that fluoresces green when complexed with DFHBI, DFHBI-1T, or other structural analogues. Useful in bulk measurements as a readout of transcription or degradation, or in microscopy for those purposes or to visualize localization.
